<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Social Media - Home</title>
  <!-- Materialize CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/css/materialize.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f5f7fb 0%, #eef5ff 100%);
      min-block-size: 100vh;
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f766e 0%, #0ea5e9 100%);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 56px 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.2);
    }

    .hero p {
      max-inline-size: 620px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-block-start: 28px;
    }

    .feature-card {
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 24px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      block-size: 100%;
    }

    .section-gap {
      margin-block-start: 28px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="white z-depth-0" style="border-block-end: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
    <div class="nav-wrapper container">
      <a href="/" class="brand-logo teal-text text-darken-2" style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700;">Social Media</a>
      <ul id="nav-mobile" class="right hide-on-med-and-down">
        <li><a href="/" class="teal-text text-darken-2">Inicio</a></li>
        <li><a href="/posts" class="teal-text text-darken-2">Posts</a></li>
        <li><a href="/posts/new" class="teal-text text-darken-2">Nuevo Post</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container" style="margin-block-start: 48px; margin-block-end: 56px;">
    <div class="hero center-align">
      <h2 style="font-weight: 800; margin-block-start: 0;">Bienvenido a Social Media 🚀</h2>
      <p class="flow-text" style="margin-block-start: 16px; margin-block-end: 0;">
        Conéctate, comparte y explora publicaciones con imágenes, enlaces y contenido creado desde MongoDB.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/posts" class="btn-large waves-effect waves-light white teal-text text-darken-2">
          <i class="material-icons left">collections</i> Ver publicaciones
        </a>
        <a href="/posts/new" class="btn-large waves-effect waves-light blue darken-2">
          <i class="material-icons left">add</i> Agregar post
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row section-gap">
      <div class="col s12 m4">
        <div class="feature-card center-align">
          <i class="material-icons large teal-text">image</i>
          <h5>Imágenes</h5>
          <p class="grey-text text-darken-1">Añade enlaces de imagen y se mostrarán directamente en cada publicación.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m4">
        <div class="feature-card center-align">
          <i class="material-icons large blue-text text-darken-2">link</i>
          <h5>Enlaces</h5>
          <p class="grey-text text-darken-1">Comparte URLs dentro del contenido o usa un enlace externo para la imagen del post.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m4">
        <div class="feature-card center-align">
          <i class="material-icons large orange-text text-darken-2">edit</i>
          <h5>Publicación rápida</h5>
          <p class="grey-text text-darken-1">Navega al formulario de posts y publica sin salir del flujo de navegación.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/js/materialize.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>